<h1><font color="#5C8526">Milestone : Algorithm for Problem 2</font></h1>
<ul><li><h2>Before any changes are made to the queries, fully qualify each attribute of the query with the current location.</h2></li>
<li><h2>Perform the relational synthesis using the algorithm for Problem 1 while keeping the original set of location information</h2></li>
<li><h2>After successful decomposition of unversal relation R and set of functional dependencies F to produce D, trickle the changes of location down to the queries </h2></li>
<li><h2>The attributes in the SELECT clause are pointed to the correct location</h2></li>
</ul></body>
